Dialogue: 0,00:00:00.23,00:02:38.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高清电影网 http://M1080.com 提供字幕下载
Dialogue: 0,00:00:53.13,00:00:58.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,红色警戒\N
Dialogue: 0,00:01:47.29,00:01:50.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世上为何有这么多战争？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:01:53.26,00:01:56.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万物为何自相残杀？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:01:57.50,00:02:00.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陆地和海洋为何互相对抗？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:02:11.48,00:02:14.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大自然是否充满仇恨？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:02:17.25,00:02:19.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,善恶是否同时存在？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:04:11.50,00:04:13.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得我母亲临终前\N
Dialogue: 0,00:04:14.93,00:04:17.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脸色苍白、形如槁木\N
Dialogue: 0,00:04:21.57,00:04:23.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我问她害不害怕？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:04:25.34,00:04:26.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她只是摇摇头\N
Dialogue: 0,00:04:28.91,00:04:31.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不敢面对她的死亡\N
Dialogue: 0,00:04:33.38,00:04:36.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不觉得她蒙主荣召\N
Dialogue: 0,00:04:36.85,00:04:38.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一件好事\N
Dialogue: 0,00:04:41.86,00:04:44.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说精神能永垂不朽\N
Dialogue: 0,00:04:44.60,00:04:45.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我没见过\N
Dialogue: 0,00:05:54.50,00:05:56.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道我死时会怎样\N
Dialogue: 0,00:05:58.50,00:06:01.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当你知道那是最后一口气\N
Dialogue: 0,00:06:01.47,00:06:03.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得是什么感觉\N
Dialogue: 0,00:06:08.28,00:06:10.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能和她一样坦然面对\N
Dialogue: 0,00:06:12.52,00:06:15.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟她一样…平静\N
Dialogue: 0,00:06:18.32,00:06:20.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当心灵得到平静\N
Dialogue: 0,00:06:20.46,00:06:22.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精神就能永垂不朽\N
Dialogue: 0,00:07:04.54,00:07:06.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里的小孩不会打架\N
Dialogue: 0,00:07:07.11,00:07:08.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候会\N
Dialogue: 0,00:07:09.44,00:07:11.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在玩耍的时候\N
Dialogue: 0,00:07:12.51,00:07:14.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总是会打架\N
Dialogue: 0,00:07:18.48,00:07:19.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他怕我吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:07:19.52,00:07:20.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一点\N
Dialogue: 0,00:07:22.92,00:07:24.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怕我吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:07:24.72,00:07:25.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怕\N
Dialogue: 0,00:07:25.72,00:07:26.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:07:26.89,00:07:29.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你看起来…\N
Dialogue: 0,00:07:30.53,00:07:32.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…像是个军人\N
Dialogue: 0,00:07:32.53,00:07:34.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我像军人？\N对
Dialogue: 0,00:07:36.17,00:07:37.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓\N
Dialogue: 0,00:07:40.67,00:07:41.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不重要\N
Dialogue: 0,00:07:45.64,00:07:46.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子累了\N
Dialogue: 0,00:07:46.91,00:07:47.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N
Dialogue: 0,00:07:48.71,00:07:51.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他游累了就会睡\N
Dialogue: 0,00:08:23.61,00:08:25.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快…快…快\N
Dialogue: 0,00:08:27.08,00:08:30.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点…快点…\N
Dialogue: 0,00:10:11.92,00:10:15.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威特，是美军的巡逻艇\N
Dialogue: 0,00:10:27.10,00:10:28.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它怎么会单独出现？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:10:55.93,00:10:58.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威特，你一点都没变\N
Dialogue: 0,00:10:59.34,00:11:00.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么也没学到\N
Dialogue: 0,00:11:03.61,00:11:05.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当别人信任你\N
Dialogue: 0,00:11:05.94,00:11:07.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就肯为他两肋插刀\N
Dialogue: 0,00:11:14.25,00:11:16.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你逃过几次兵？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:11:19.26,00:11:21.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你当兵六年了\N
Dialogue: 0,00:11:22.86,00:11:24.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果要学聪明\N
Dialogue: 0,00:11:24.86,00:11:27.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在该是时候了\N
Dialogue: 0,00:11:28.67,00:11:30.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能都当聪明人\N
Dialogue: 0,00:11:32.00,00:11:35.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错，真可惜，看看你\N
Dialogue: 0,00:11:41.28,00:11:45.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在我的连队不能乖乖服役\N
Dialogue: 0,00:11:47.18,00:11:51.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这世上当不了好军人\N
Dialogue: 0,00:11:54.02,00:11:56.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是C连，我是副连长\N
Dialogue: 0,00:11:56.33,00:11:58.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史塔洛上尉是连长\N
Dialogue: 0,00:11:59.16,00:12:02.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我管事，谁都不能抗命\N
Dialogue: 0,00:12:03.27,00:12:05.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只是一张吃饭的嘴\N
Dialogue: 0,00:12:08.64,00:12:10.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你本来得接受军事审判\N
Dialogue: 0,00:12:12.08,00:12:16.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算你走运，我替你另做安排\N
Dialogue: 0,00:12:18.05,00:12:20.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我派你到违纪部队\N
Dialogue: 0,00:12:21.39,00:12:25.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当担架兵，照顾伤兵\N
Dialogue: 0,00:12:27.06,00:12:29.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能接受任何处罚\N
Dialogue: 0,00:12:30.16,00:12:32.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人就比你好两倍\N
Dialogue: 0,00:12:44.04,00:12:45.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这个世界\N
Dialogue: 0,00:12:46.91,00:12:49.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个人\N
Dialogue: 0,00:12:50.15,00:12:51.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本微不足道\N
Dialogue: 0,00:12:55.25,00:12:58.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有这一个世界\N
Dialogue: 0,00:13:01.36,00:13:02.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你错了，副连长\N
Dialogue: 0,00:13:06.16,00:13:08.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我见过另一个世界\N
Dialogue: 0,00:13:13.87,00:13:18.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候我觉得那是我的想像\N
Dialogue: 0,00:13:20.38,00:13:24.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你的看法不同\N
Dialogue: 0,00:13:34.83,00:13:38.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界在自我毁灭\N
Dialogue: 0,00:13:41.27,00:13:45.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只能睁一只眼闭一只眼\N
Dialogue: 0,00:13:46.37,00:13:47.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为自己着想\N
Dialogue: 0,00:14:00.52,00:14:02.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可能是你最好的朋友\N
Dialogue: 0,00:14:05.49,00:14:06.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己都不知道\N
Dialogue: 0,00:14:39.29,00:14:41.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他恨透你了\N
Dialogue: 0,00:14:46.30,00:14:48.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不觉得他恨我\N
Dialogue: 0,00:14:48.47,00:14:49.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不恨他\N
Dialogue: 0,00:15:30.57,00:15:32.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱C连弟兄\N
Dialogue: 0,00:15:37.55,00:15:38.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是我的家人\N
Dialogue: 0,00:16:05.08,00:16:06.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这座岛叫“顽石”\N
Dialogue: 0,00:16:06.88,00:16:10.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本无人占领\N后来让日军盖了机场
Dialogue: 0,00:16:10.21,00:16:12.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主要战区在这里\N
Dialogue: 0,00:16:12.32,00:16:15.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是攻击澳洲的跳板\N
Dialogue: 0,00:16:15.12,00:16:17.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也控制进攻美国的海道\N
Dialogue: 0,00:16:17.45,00:16:20.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若要阻止日军攻占南太平洋\N
Dialogue: 0,00:16:20.99,00:16:22.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就得在这里开战\N
Dialogue: 0,00:16:24.26,00:16:26.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陆战队试过，现在轮到我们\N
Dialogue: 0,00:16:29.27,00:16:31.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拼死拼活\N
Dialogue: 0,00:16:32.40,00:16:34.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽量迎合将军\N
Dialogue: 0,00:16:36.67,00:16:38.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放低身段\N
Dialogue: 0,00:16:40.64,00:16:43.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为他们、为我家人\N
Dialogue: 0,00:16:45.28,00:16:47.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我的家\N
Dialogue: 0,00:16:48.05,00:16:49.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很钦佩你，上校\N
Dialogue: 0,00:16:50.02,00:16:51.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，长官\N
Dialogue: 0,00:16:51.36,00:16:53.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这年纪的军官早退休了\N
Dialogue: 0,00:16:54.46,00:16:55.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是好军人\N
Dialogue: 0,00:16:56.96,00:16:59.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,部队需要你这种成熟的将官\N
Dialogue: 0,00:17:01.40,00:17:04.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有好的中士和中校\N
Dialogue: 0,00:17:04.57,00:17:08.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们当了上校，就想当将军\N
Dialogue: 0,00:17:08.34,00:17:09.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,于是成为政客\N
Dialogue: 0,00:17:10.31,00:17:12.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只会拍上司的马屁\N
Dialogue: 0,00:17:14.11,00:17:17.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很难坚持原则\N
Dialogue: 0,00:17:17.38,00:17:18.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说得对，长官\N
Dialogue: 0,00:17:18.58,00:17:21.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上将会注意我的表现\N
Dialogue: 0,00:17:21.52,00:17:23.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定有人盯着你\N
Dialogue: 0,00:17:25.02,00:17:26.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像只猎鹰\N
Dialogue: 0,00:17:27.52,00:17:30.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总是有人想抢你的功劳\N
Dialogue: 0,00:17:42.44,00:17:43.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有儿子吗，上校？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:17:43.64,00:17:44.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有的，长官\N
Dialogue: 0,00:17:44.58,00:17:45.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N
Dialogue: 0,00:17:45.51,00:17:49.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能让子孙打这场烂仗\N
Dialogue: 0,00:17:49.45,00:17:51.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错，是不能\N
Dialogue: 0,00:17:51.15,00:17:52.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就全力攻敌\N
Dialogue: 0,00:17:53.35,00:17:55.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把敌人赶尽杀绝，抢下机场\N
Dialogue: 0,00:17:56.32,00:17:57.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，长官\N
Dialogue: 0,00:17:58.22,00:17:59.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有想过\N
Dialogue: 0,00:18:00.06,00:18:04.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日军为何在这儿盖机场？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:18:05.20,00:18:08.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们对大局不太清楚\N
Dialogue: 0,00:18:08.53,00:18:09.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认为呢？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:18:09.80,00:18:12.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从不想这种问题\N
Dialogue: 0,00:18:13.17,00:18:14.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很谦虚\N
Dialogue: 0,00:18:17.04,00:18:20.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人要这座岛…除了你\N
Dialogue: 0,00:18:21.15,00:18:22.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有多大的决心？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:18:23.61,00:18:25.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会全力以赴\N
Dialogue: 0,00:18:29.22,00:18:33.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家人为我做的牺牲\N
Dialogue: 0,00:18:35.03,00:18:37.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像覆水难收\N
Dialogue: 0,00:18:43.50,00:18:46.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本来能好好爱他们\N
Dialogue: 0,00:19:01.12,00:19:02.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太迟了\N
Dialogue: 0,00:19:07.83,00:19:09.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的心已死\N
Dialogue: 0,00:19:11.26,00:19:13.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像树木一样慢慢凋零\N
Dialogue: 0,00:19:15.60,00:19:17.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你感觉得到吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:19:18.44,00:19:19.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，长官\N
Dialogue: 0,00:19:24.54,00:19:25.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，长官\N
Dialogue: 0,00:19:48.43,00:19:51.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,权力越大，恐惧越深\N
Dialogue: 0,00:20:08.79,00:20:11.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是感到害怕\N
Dialogue: 0,00:20:13.29,00:20:14.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无法控制\N
Dialogue: 0,00:20:14.86,00:20:18.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小时候我继父常用砖块打我\N
Dialogue: 0,00:20:18.40,00:20:21.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好怕，老是躲起来\N
Dialogue: 0,00:20:21.70,00:20:24.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时常睡在鸡窝\N
Dialogue: 0,00:20:24.90,00:20:29.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为我不会再害怕\N
Dialogue: 0,00:20:30.54,00:20:34.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在我分秒都在害怕\N
Dialogue: 0,00:20:34.75,00:20:37.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要登陆\N
Dialogue: 0,00:20:37.35,00:20:38.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定会遭到空袭\N
Dialogue: 0,00:20:39.22,00:20:40.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会阵亡在滩头\N
Dialogue: 0,00:20:42.55,00:20:46.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船就像漂流的坟墓\N
Dialogue: 0,00:20:46.66,00:20:47.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么，小子？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:20:47.82,00:20:50.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我退伍后想买一辆车\N
Dialogue: 0,00:20:52.33,00:20:53.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:20:53.30,00:20:54.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾德华崔恩\N
Dialogue: 0,00:20:54.87,00:20:55.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,崔恩\N
Dialogue: 0,00:20:56.30,00:21:02.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有上帝和死亡是永恒的\N
Dialogue: 0,00:21:02.31,00:21:03.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只担心这些\N
Dialogue: 0,00:21:03.71,00:21:07.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这场战争不是你我的终点\N
Dialogue: 0,00:21:07.98,00:21:09.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会遭到空袭吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:21:09.38,00:21:10.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么知道？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:21:10.95,00:21:15.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别的大兵说上次进攻就没有\N
Dialogue: 0,00:21:15.92,00:21:19.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上上一次他们差点被炸死\N
Dialogue: 0,00:21:19.86,00:21:21.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要我怎么说\N
Dialogue: 0,00:21:21.59,00:21:25.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多谢了，你什么也没说\N
Dialogue: 0,00:21:25.50,00:21:26.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我要告诉你\N
Dialogue: 0,00:21:26.76,00:21:30.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在船上就像是死鸭子\N
Dialogue: 0,00:21:30.80,00:21:32.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早就知道\N
Dialogue: 0,00:21:32.94,00:21:36.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好想一想，提尔，好好地想\N
Dialogue: 0,00:21:37.57,00:21:39.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不看好戏吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:21:39.24,00:21:40.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没兴趣\N
Dialogue: 0,00:21:40.78,00:21:42.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太挤了\N
Dialogue: 0,00:21:42.85,00:21:45.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算不挤我也不想看\N
Dialogue: 0,00:21:45.32,00:21:47.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去拿那把手枪\N
Dialogue: 0,00:21:47.95,00:21:49.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？开心点\N
Dialogue: 0,00:21:49.55,00:21:51.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，开心点\N
Dialogue: 0,00:21:52.26,00:21:56.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有手枪才能对付日本武士刀\N
Dialogue: 0,00:21:56.69,00:22:03.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快开门，给我开门…\N
Dialogue: 0,00:22:23.49,00:22:28.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我入伍时没想到会有这下场\N
Dialogue: 0,00:22:28.06,00:22:30.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么知道会打仗？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:22:31.03,00:22:32.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是说说\N
Dialogue: 0,00:22:36.60,00:22:39.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道C连最衰了\N
Dialogue: 0,00:22:39.94,00:22:42.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道是谁的错\N
Dialogue: 0,00:22:43.07,00:22:44.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是咱们的连长\N
Dialogue: 0,00:22:45.04,00:22:49.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他害大家被派上这艘鬼船\N
Dialogue: 0,00:22:49.05,00:22:51.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是第四批登陆部队\N
Dialogue: 0,00:23:08.80,00:23:09.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连长好\N
Dialogue: 0,00:23:55.08,00:23:58.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,档案说你在战前是军官\N
Dialogue: 0,00:23:59.45,00:24:00.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会变成二等兵？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:24:01.72,00:24:02.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我太太\N
Dialogue: 0,00:24:04.45,00:24:06.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本来在工兵部队\N
Dialogue: 0,00:24:07.96,00:24:10.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和她从来没分开过\N
Dialogue: 0,00:24:11.36,00:24:12.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连一晚都没有\N
Dialogue: 0,00:24:13.96,00:24:16.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忍受了四个月\N
Dialogue: 0,00:24:16.90,00:24:18.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后终于放弃\N
Dialogue: 0,00:24:19.94,00:24:21.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辞职不干\N
Dialogue: 0,00:24:23.01,00:24:25.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被送回美国\N
Dialogue: 0,00:24:25.81,00:24:28.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远不能当军官\N
Dialogue: 0,00:24:28.95,00:24:31.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们说要征召我入伍\N
Dialogue: 0,00:24:31.92,00:24:34.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我当步兵\N
Dialogue: 0,00:24:35.49,00:24:36.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些浑蛋\N
Dialogue: 0,00:24:37.89,00:24:39.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不怪他们\N
Dialogue: 0,00:24:42.39,00:24:43.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在哪里？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:24:45.60,00:24:46.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在家里\N
Dialogue: 0,00:25:00.98,00:25:03.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我并不怕死\N
Dialogue: 0,00:25:06.45,00:25:08.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我已属于\N
Dialogue: 0,00:25:09.99,00:25:13.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快…快…快…\N
Dialogue: 0,00:25:22.20,00:25:24.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点…\N
Dialogue: 0,00:25:24.60,00:25:28.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我先走，我会等的\N
Dialogue: 0,00:25:29.97,00:25:32.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在死亡的另一边\N
Dialogue: 0,00:25:39.82,00:25:40.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔，戴上头盔\N
Dialogue: 0,00:25:42.95,00:25:44.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与我同在\N
Dialogue: 0,00:25:54.80,00:25:56.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,压力很大，对吧？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:25:56.17,00:25:57.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，长官\N
Dialogue: 0,00:25:59.50,00:26:00.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你，上尉\N
Dialogue: 0,00:26:01.17,00:26:05.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你知道我很支持你\N
Dialogue: 0,00:26:07.24,00:26:11.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先逼近敌区，我会赶上来\N
Dialogue: 0,00:26:11.28,00:26:12.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由你全权指挥\N
Dialogue: 0,00:26:13.08,00:26:15.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开，让开\N
Dialogue: 0,00:26:16.02,00:26:17.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要过去\N
Dialogue: 0,00:26:17.22,00:26:20.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,班长马上报到\N
Dialogue: 0,00:26:20.19,00:26:21.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里\N
Dialogue: 0,00:26:23.56,00:26:25.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备上登陆船\N
Dialogue: 0,00:27:38.57,00:27:40.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在天上的父\N
Dialogue: 0,00:27:42.07,00:27:44.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,免我们的债如同我们免人的债\N
Dialogue: 0,00:27:45.31,00:27:49.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,国度权柄荣耀全是您的，阿门\N
Dialogue: 0,00:28:02.19,00:28:03.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们很幸运\N
Dialogue: 0,00:28:04.09,00:28:06.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,运输船刚被日军发现\N
Dialogue: 0,00:28:06.90,00:28:08.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸好你们下来了\N
Dialogue: 0,00:28:18.11,00:28:22.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深呼吸，你得深呼吸\N
Dialogue: 0,00:28:52.84,00:28:53.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是C连吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:28:54.21,00:28:55.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们深入内陆一英里\N
Dialogue: 0,00:28:55.35,00:28:56.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么也没有\N
Dialogue: 0,00:28:56.65,00:28:59.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个礼拜都没动静\N
Dialogue: 0,00:28:59.65,00:29:03.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无人伤亡，日军大概都跑了\N
Dialogue: 0,00:29:03.32,00:29:05.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们受迫击炮攻击，无人伤亡\N
Dialogue: 0,00:29:06.16,00:29:07.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这地方很不可思议\N
Dialogue: 0,00:29:10.09,00:29:12.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有鱼住在树上\N
Dialogue: 0,00:29:16.37,00:29:19.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指挥部好像没搞清楚状况\N
Dialogue: 0,00:30:52.43,00:30:56.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您化身为宇宙万物\N
Dialogue: 0,00:31:28.20,00:31:31.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万物皆难逃一死\N
Dialogue: 0,00:31:37.01,00:31:40.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您也是生命的泉源\N
Dialogue: 0,00:32:05.00,00:32:06.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您充满荣耀\N
Dialogue: 0,00:32:10.24,00:32:11.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慈悲\N
Dialogue: 0,00:32:13.94,00:32:15.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宁静\N
Dialogue: 0,00:32:18.01,00:32:19.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真理\N
Dialogue: 0,00:32:26.86,00:32:29.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您能安抚人心\N
Dialogue: 0,00:32:32.03,00:32:33.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给人们谅解\N
Dialogue: 0,00:32:35.97,00:32:37.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和勇气\N
Dialogue: 0,00:32:42.57,00:32:44.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使人得到满足\N
Dialogue: 0,00:36:32.17,00:36:34.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许每个人都有共同的灵魂\N
Dialogue: 0,00:36:34.60,00:36:36.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和相同的命运\N
Dialogue: 0,00:36:39.61,00:36:41.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每张脸孔都是同一个人\N
Dialogue: 0,00:36:43.45,00:36:45.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个大我\N
Dialogue: 0,00:37:19.68,00:37:23.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都想获得救赎\N
Dialogue: 0,00:37:29.56,00:37:33.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像炭火般燃烧生命\N
Dialogue: 0,00:38:06.43,00:38:08.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要攻上那座山头\N
Dialogue: 0,00:38:12.54,00:38:14.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,办不到，上校\N
Dialogue: 0,00:38:14.97,00:38:17.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们无法包抄敌军\N
Dialogue: 0,00:38:17.64,00:38:19.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左边的悬崖底下是河流\N
Dialogue: 0,00:38:19.61,00:38:21.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日军守住丛林\N
Dialogue: 0,00:38:21.54,00:38:23.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得正面突袭\N
Dialogue: 0,00:38:26.32,00:38:28.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,食用水怎么办？山上没清水\N
Dialogue: 0,00:38:28.65,00:38:31.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的弟兄都因为脱水昏倒\N
Dialogue: 0,00:38:38.83,00:38:42.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们能发牢骚就能打仗\N
Dialogue: 0,00:38:56.51,00:38:58.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并肩前进，第三排留守\N
Dialogue: 0,00:39:00.42,00:39:03.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得越过三个山丘\N
Dialogue: 0,00:39:03.95,00:39:06.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后再攻下山头\N
Dialogue: 0,00:39:17.80,00:39:20.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上校说不能采取包抄攻势\N
Dialogue: 0,00:39:20.80,00:39:23.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得正面突袭\N
Dialogue: 0,00:39:25.51,00:39:26.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怀特\N是
Dialogue: 0,00:39:27.41,00:39:29.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到山坡前面吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:39:29.38,00:39:30.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到了\N
Dialogue: 0,00:39:30.08,00:39:31.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等你攻上山坡\N
Dialogue: 0,00:39:31.91,00:39:35.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到敌军据点然后消灭他们\N
Dialogue: 0,00:39:39.29,00:39:43.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那儿一定有敌军守住\N
Dialogue: 0,00:40:36.65,00:40:39.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主啊，您在吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:40:52.86,00:40:54.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别让我背叛您\N
Dialogue: 0,00:40:58.70,00:41:00.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别让我背叛我的弟兄\N
Dialogue: 0,00:41:08.68,00:41:10.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您让我充满信心\N和希望
Dialogue: 0,00:41:23.56,00:41:26.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（希腊语）\N
Dialogue: 0,00:41:26.80,00:41:28.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玫瑰般的黎明\N
Dialogue: 0,00:41:30.73,00:41:34.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是希腊人\N读过荷马的史诗吗？
Dialogue: 0,00:41:35.10,00:41:38.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在西点军校读过希腊原文\N
Dialogue: 0,00:41:40.48,00:41:42.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有多少炮兵支援火力？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:41:43.05,00:41:45.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两组105榴弹炮\N
Dialogue: 0,00:41:46.12,00:41:47.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一点都没有用\N
Dialogue: 0,00:41:47.88,00:41:49.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过能鼓舞士气\N
Dialogue: 0,00:41:49.99,00:41:52.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日军会被炸得很难看\N
Dialogue: 0,00:42:46.48,00:42:47.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弟兄们\N
Dialogue: 0,00:42:48.71,00:42:49.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备上吧\N
Dialogue: 0,00:42:50.21,00:42:51.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每组十人攻上山头\N
Dialogue: 0,00:42:53.78,00:42:56.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快速前进才不会成为目标\N
Dialogue: 0,00:42:58.52,00:43:00.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一路跑上去\N
Dialogue: 0,00:43:00.76,00:43:02.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们被选上，别无选择\N
Dialogue: 0,00:43:02.06,00:43:04.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非去不可\N
Dialogue: 0,00:43:07.53,00:43:09.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我亲自带领先锋队\N
Dialogue: 0,00:43:09.53,00:43:10.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要戴尔\N
Dialogue: 0,00:43:10.90,00:43:11.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是\N
Dialogue: 0,00:43:12.17,00:43:14.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫弟兄在山坡集合\N
Dialogue: 0,00:43:20.58,00:43:22.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五分钟后出发\N
Dialogue: 0,00:43:24.08,00:43:25.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N
Dialogue: 0,00:43:29.52,00:43:30.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西寇\N
Dialogue: 0,00:43:32.09,00:43:33.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:43:33.19,00:43:34.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的肚子好痛\N
Dialogue: 0,00:43:35.16,00:43:37.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起来，小心我踢扁你\N
Dialogue: 0,00:43:37.99,00:43:40.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我站不起来\N
Dialogue: 0,00:43:40.26,00:43:41.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我生病了\N
Dialogue: 0,00:43:43.93,00:43:44.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我病了\N
Dialogue: 0,00:43:45.00,00:43:46.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没有病，起来\N
Dialogue: 0,00:43:51.07,00:43:52.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西寇，怎么了？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:43:52.64,00:43:53.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得\N
Dialogue: 0,00:43:54.24,00:43:57.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好痛，好像是胃痉挛\N
Dialogue: 0,00:43:57.85,00:44:00.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我病了，坐不起来\N
Dialogue: 0,00:44:04.05,00:44:05.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我起来\N
Dialogue: 0,00:44:05.22,00:44:06.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别逼他了\N
Dialogue: 0,00:44:06.19,00:44:08.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁要替我扛步枪？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:44:08.09,00:44:09.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我带你找医官\N
Dialogue: 0,00:44:09.89,00:44:11.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，副连长\N
Dialogue: 0,00:44:14.76,00:44:16.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别跟我争\N
Dialogue: 0,00:44:16.90,00:44:18.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝好运，柯克\N
Dialogue: 0,00:45:46.19,00:45:47.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许他们撤退了\N
Dialogue: 0,00:47:59.29,00:48:02.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快趴下！趴下来！\N
Dialogue: 0,00:48:08.00,00:48:10.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点…冷静点…\N
Dialogue: 0,00:48:16.17,00:48:17.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,担架兵\N
Dialogue: 0,00:48:33.46,00:48:34.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这儿\N
Dialogue: 0,00:48:35.32,00:48:36.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这儿\N
Dialogue: 0,00:48:38.19,00:48:39.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去救那弟兄\N
Dialogue: 0,00:48:39.60,00:48:41.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经有八、九名伤兵…\N
Dialogue: 0,00:48:41.46,00:48:43.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别跟我争，我要救他\N
Dialogue: 0,00:48:43.87,00:48:45.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管不了他们了\N
Dialogue: 0,00:48:45.83,00:48:47.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死，全都要救\N
Dialogue: 0,00:48:47.30,00:48:48.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是指挥官\N
Dialogue: 0,00:48:49.10,00:48:50.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道你是连长吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:48:50.97,00:48:53.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是说别人伤得更重\N
Dialogue: 0,00:48:55.14,00:48:57.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二等兵，听我的命令\N
Dialogue: 0,00:49:00.25,00:49:01.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好，副连长\N
Dialogue: 0,00:49:03.89,00:49:05.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要救谁？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:49:07.02,00:49:08.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该是贾克\N
Dialogue: 0,00:49:09.29,00:49:10.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贾克老兄\N
Dialogue: 0,00:49:10.99,00:49:13.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是倒霉\N
Dialogue: 0,00:49:14.13,00:49:15.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长官\N
Dialogue: 0,00:49:16.23,00:49:22.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把贾克抬回去我能回来吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:49:22.64,00:49:25.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，你要得到许可\N
Dialogue: 0,00:49:25.07,00:49:26.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然，我的步枪\N
Dialogue: 0,00:49:29.51,00:49:32.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼基，你还活着\N
Dialogue: 0,00:49:32.91,00:49:34.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续前进\N
Dialogue: 0,00:49:36.02,00:49:37.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，史塔洛\N
Dialogue: 0,00:49:37.35,00:49:41.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久没见到这么猛烈的攻击\N
Dialogue: 0,00:49:42.16,00:49:45.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你指挥得很好\N
Dialogue: 0,00:49:45.06,00:49:47.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会请营长给你功勋\N
Dialogue: 0,00:49:47.26,00:49:49.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怀特排长的表现也很棒\N
Dialogue: 0,00:49:49.20,00:49:50.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，长官\N
Dialogue: 0,00:49:50.97,00:49:54.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,派第二排增援也很聪明\N
Dialogue: 0,00:49:54.40,00:49:58.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就快攻上去了，伤亡不惨重\N
Dialogue: 0,00:49:58.17,00:49:59.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布兰也不错\N
Dialogue: 0,00:49:59.94,00:50:03.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们发现多少据点？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:50:03.31,00:50:04.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消灭了多少？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:50:05.11,00:50:08.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中午就应该能攻上山头\N
Dialogue: 0,00:50:10.95,00:50:13.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史塔洛，你在吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:50:13.52,00:50:15.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在，长官\N
Dialogue: 0,00:50:15.92,00:50:18.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们发现多少据点？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:50:18.56,00:50:20.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消灭了多少？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:50:22.10,00:50:23.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们…\N
Dialogue: 0,00:50:24.00,00:50:25.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N
Dialogue: 0,00:50:26.10,00:50:30.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？你怎么会不知道？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:50:31.17,00:50:35.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在第一座山丘后面\N
Dialogue: 0,00:50:35.31,00:50:37.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我站起来招手吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:50:37.68,00:50:40.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了，你得想办法\N
Dialogue: 0,00:50:40.95,00:50:43.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快上去看看情况如何\N
Dialogue: 0,00:50:43.69,00:50:46.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我就要你攻下山头\N
Dialogue: 0,00:50:46.42,00:50:49.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上将一早就要来查看\N
Dialogue: 0,00:50:49.12,00:50:52.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神来，完毕\N
Dialogue: 0,00:51:18.62,00:51:19.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上吧\N
Dialogue: 0,00:51:39.24,00:51:40.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯克\N
Dialogue: 0,00:51:41.68,00:51:43.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:51:44.01,00:51:45.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得撤退\N
Dialogue: 0,00:51:45.68,00:51:47.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N
Dialogue: 0,00:51:47.75,00:51:49.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布兰死了\N
Dialogue: 0,00:51:50.19,00:51:51.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得指挥\N
Dialogue: 0,00:51:55.19,00:51:58.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美国佬，我们看到你们\N
Dialogue: 0,00:51:58.69,00:52:00.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,东条英机去死\N
Dialogue: 0,00:52:01.20,00:52:04.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗斯福去死\N
Dialogue: 0,00:52:39.87,00:52:41.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打到他了\N
Dialogue: 0,00:53:00.09,00:53:01.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我杀死一个人\N
Dialogue: 0,00:53:02.09,00:53:03.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昆恩\N
Dialogue: 0,00:53:04.89,00:53:06.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昆恩，你在吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:53:06.76,00:53:11.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀人比强暴还要严重\N
Dialogue: 0,00:53:11.20,00:53:14.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到日本鬼子离开左边吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:53:14.40,00:53:15.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人能把我怎样\N
Dialogue: 0,00:53:15.77,00:53:17.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么也没看到\N
Dialogue: 0,00:53:17.81,00:53:20.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抬起头来看看\N
Dialogue: 0,00:53:22.28,00:53:23.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说真的\N
Dialogue: 0,00:53:24.58,00:53:27.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有七个日兵离开左边\N
Dialogue: 0,00:53:28.75,00:53:30.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打中一个\N
Dialogue: 0,00:53:31.25,00:53:32.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又怎样？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:53:32.52,00:53:34.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们要撤退\N
Dialogue: 0,00:53:38.23,00:53:40.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许该去告诉连长\N
Dialogue: 0,00:53:40.46,00:53:42.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想去吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:53:47.90,00:53:50.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我命令你别乱动\N
Dialogue: 0,00:54:14.43,00:54:15.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趴下\N
Dialogue: 0,00:54:23.87,00:54:25.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趴低点\N
Dialogue: 0,00:54:52.53,00:54:56.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上…上…上…\N
Dialogue: 0,00:55:37.58,00:55:38.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在怎么办？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:55:39.91,00:55:41.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这儿等\N
Dialogue: 0,00:55:41.55,00:55:43.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许会有人来支援\N
Dialogue: 0,00:55:44.29,00:55:45.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做什么？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:55:45.42,00:55:48.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻下敌军的据点呀\N
Dialogue: 0,00:55:48.72,00:55:50.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要继续进攻？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:55:50.63,00:55:51.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道\N
Dialogue: 0,00:55:51.93,00:55:54.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能直接进攻山头\N
Dialogue: 0,00:55:54.60,00:55:56.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过如果有支援\N
Dialogue: 0,00:55:56.80,00:56:00.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能试着除掉机关枪\N
Dialogue: 0,00:56:00.97,00:56:02.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总比冒死退回去好\N
Dialogue: 0,00:56:02.90,00:56:04.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人来了\N他们来了
Dialogue: 0,00:56:11.91,00:56:16.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们为什么不全力进攻？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:56:16.95,00:56:18.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许他们落了单\N
Dialogue: 0,00:56:19.82,00:56:21.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许他们想上西天\N
Dialogue: 0,00:56:24.56,00:56:25.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人来了\N
Dialogue: 0,00:56:36.81,00:56:38.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:56:38.61,00:56:39.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N
Dialogue: 0,00:56:42.38,00:56:43.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我炸到屁股\N
Dialogue: 0,00:56:44.68,00:56:46.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把屁股炸掉了\N
Dialogue: 0,00:56:47.78,00:56:48.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趴下来\N
Dialogue: 0,00:56:48.92,00:56:51.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会这么衰？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:56:52.79,00:56:54.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只拔到保险栓\N
Dialogue: 0,00:56:55.76,00:56:57.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,写信给我老婆\N
Dialogue: 0,00:56:58.03,00:57:00.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉她我死得很光荣\N
Dialogue: 0,00:57:00.53,00:57:02.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会死的\N
Dialogue: 0,00:57:02.43,00:57:04.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别骗我\N
Dialogue: 0,00:57:08.10,00:57:11.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我全身是泥，帮我擦掉\N
Dialogue: 0,00:57:15.48,00:57:17.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会写信给她\N
Dialogue: 0,00:57:20.92,00:57:24.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的水壶还有水，拿去吧\N
Dialogue: 0,00:57:29.82,00:57:31.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许这样最好\N
Dialogue: 0,00:57:32.63,00:57:34.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的下面被炸烂\N
Dialogue: 0,00:57:36.06,00:57:37.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能搞了\N
Dialogue: 0,00:57:40.70,00:57:46.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在哪儿？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:57:49.88,00:57:51.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会有事\N
Dialogue: 0,00:57:52.15,00:57:53.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你死了\N
Dialogue: 0,00:57:54.42,00:57:56.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没有对不起弟兄\N
Dialogue: 0,00:57:56.95,00:57:59.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你不扑上去\N
Dialogue: 0,00:57:59.89,00:58:01.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们全都会死\N
Dialogue: 0,00:58:01.82,00:58:03.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好冷\N
Dialogue: 0,00:58:05.79,00:58:07.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好冷\N
Dialogue: 0,00:58:09.86,00:58:11.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我快冷死了\N
Dialogue: 0,00:59:06.45,00:59:08.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要写信给他老婆？\N
Dialogue: 0,00:59:10.02,00:59:11.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不要\N
Dialogue: 0,00:59:12.46,00:59:14.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又不认识她\N
Dialogue: 0,00:59:14.93,00:59:17.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是连长的事\N
Dialogue: 0,00:59:17.67,00:59:19.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别傻了，我不会写信\N
Dialogue: 0,00:59:19.70,00:59:21.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你答应过他\N
Dialogue: 0,00:59:21.94,00:59:24.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他快死了，我得那么说\N
Dialogue: 0,00:59:26.87,00:59:28.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人得写信给她\N
Dialogue: 0,00:59:28.58,00:59:31.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你写给她吧\N
Dialogue: 0,00:59:40.66,00:59:42.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:01:02.00,01:01:03.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救救我\N
Dialogue: 0,01:01:03.30,01:01:04.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他没救了\N
Dialogue: 0,01:01:05.27,01:01:07.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁也救不了他\N
Dialogue: 0,01:01:08.28,01:01:09.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不必去了\N
Dialogue: 0,01:01:09.81,01:01:12.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以替他注射吗啡\N
Dialogue: 0,01:01:13.11,01:01:14.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能让他安静吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:01:14.32,01:01:16.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能，我可以打两针\N
Dialogue: 0,01:01:16.75,01:01:19.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留三、四针给他自己打\N
Dialogue: 0,01:01:22.16,01:01:24.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能一次打完吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:01:42.61,01:01:44.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们都会死\N
Dialogue: 0,01:01:46.61,01:01:48.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们全都会没命\N
Dialogue: 0,01:01:50.15,01:01:53.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的十二名弟兄都死了\N
Dialogue: 0,01:01:54.89,01:01:58.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都挂了，太疯狂了\N
Dialogue: 0,01:01:58.33,01:02:02.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫他们勇往直前\N
Dialogue: 0,01:02:03.97,01:02:06.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认得你…\N
Dialogue: 0,01:02:06.83,01:02:08.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副连长\N
Dialogue: 0,01:02:08.44,01:02:12.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里谁指挥？别放走他\N
Dialogue: 0,01:02:12.81,01:02:15.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要走，我要走\N
Dialogue: 0,01:02:15.98,01:02:19.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两只脚，快走，走啊\N
Dialogue: 0,01:02:19.28,01:02:21.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了…\N
Dialogue: 0,01:02:21.92,01:02:24.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我，别看我\N
Dialogue: 0,01:02:24.35,01:02:26.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我，我走了\N
Dialogue: 0,01:02:48.68,01:02:54.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救救我，救救我\N
Dialogue: 0,01:02:54.05,01:02:56.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还好吧，小子？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:02:56.15,01:02:57.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来救你了，提拉\N
Dialogue: 0,01:02:57.92,01:02:59.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安静点\N
Dialogue: 0,01:02:59.19,01:03:03.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去你的，我快死了\N
Dialogue: 0,01:03:03.99,01:03:06.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就安静地等死\N
Dialogue: 0,01:03:07.90,01:03:08.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能救我吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:03:08.96,01:03:10.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会带你回去\N
Dialogue: 0,01:03:15.27,01:03:18.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放我下来…\N
Dialogue: 0,01:03:23.24,01:03:28.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别管我，你别管我\N
Dialogue: 0,01:03:35.29,01:03:39.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再多给我一点\N
Dialogue: 0,01:03:39.13,01:03:46.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多给我一点…\N
Dialogue: 0,01:03:46.90,01:03:48.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\N
Dialogue: 0,01:03:57.11,01:04:02.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见…再见…\N
Dialogue: 0,01:04:03.32,01:04:04.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见了，小子\N
Dialogue: 0,01:04:05.05,01:04:06.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见，副连长\N
Dialogue: 0,01:04:25.07,01:04:28.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸好部队不必只靠一个大兵\N
Dialogue: 0,01:04:33.11,01:04:36.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我用望远镜看到经过\N
Dialogue: 0,01:04:36.38,01:04:38.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会请营长表扬你\N
Dialogue: 0,01:04:38.79,01:04:40.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要替你争取银星勋章\N
Dialogue: 0,01:04:41.19,01:04:46.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你再说下去我就把你揍扁\N
Dialogue: 0,01:04:47.19,01:04:51.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去争取勋章，我马上辞职\N
Dialogue: 0,01:04:51.80,01:04:56.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你一个人指挥这个烂部队\N
Dialogue: 0,01:04:56.57,01:04:58.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懂不懂？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:04:59.41,01:05:03.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,权力！打仗全是为了权力\N
Dialogue: 0,01:05:18.33,01:05:20.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什么鬼？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:05:20.29,01:05:22.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上派人支援他们\N
Dialogue: 0,01:05:23.00,01:05:24.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在干嘛？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:05:24.50,01:05:27.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躺在那里做什么？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:05:27.40,01:05:30.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们应该去消灭机关枪\N
Dialogue: 0,01:05:31.31,01:05:34.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想你不明白，长官\N
Dialogue: 0,01:05:34.18,01:05:37.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的伤亡惨重\N
Dialogue: 0,01:05:37.38,01:05:41.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一个人的肠子被打出来\N
Dialogue: 0,01:05:41.52,01:05:42.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死得很惨\N
Dialogue: 0,01:05:42.52,01:05:45.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，到底有没有支援？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:05:45.85,01:05:51.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一排有两个班可以支援\N
Dialogue: 0,01:05:51.36,01:05:53.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么，两个班？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:05:54.53,01:05:58.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死，我叫你支援就照办\N
Dialogue: 0,01:05:58.43,01:06:02.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上派全体弟兄攻上去\N
Dialogue: 0,01:06:02.17,01:06:04.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一排也得去\N
Dialogue: 0,01:06:04.04,01:06:06.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到他们躺着不动\N
Dialogue: 0,01:06:06.21,01:06:09.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,派人上去，命令他们进攻\N
Dialogue: 0,01:06:09.28,01:06:11.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命令他们侧攻\N
Dialogue: 0,01:06:11.41,01:06:14.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后叫第二排攻上山头\N
Dialogue: 0,01:06:14.22,01:06:15.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫他们直接攻上去\N
Dialogue: 0,01:06:16.02,01:06:19.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上进攻\N
Dialogue: 0,01:06:19.92,01:06:24.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老天，我得教你吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:06:24.69,01:06:26.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的弟兄快被射死了\N
Dialogue: 0,01:06:26.13,01:06:29.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上校，你不明白这里的情况\N
Dialogue: 0,01:06:29.70,01:06:32.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光凭这一连不能攻下山头\N
Dialogue: 0,01:06:33.17,01:06:36.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌军防守严密、火力太强\N
Dialogue: 0,01:06:36.57,01:06:40.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面有座碉堡，我们看不到\N
Dialogue: 0,01:06:40.54,01:06:42.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它把我的弟兄打得很惨\N
Dialogue: 0,01:06:45.25,01:06:48.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你准许我先派人\N
Dialogue: 0,01:06:48.68,01:06:51.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进入右翼的丛林搜查\N
Dialogue: 0,01:06:51.39,01:06:55.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从右翼包抄应该能攻下山头\N
Dialogue: 0,01:06:55.39,01:06:59.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，该死，不能包抄\N
Dialogue: 0,01:06:59.96,01:07:03.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我说，你不能带弟兄\N
Dialogue: 0,01:07:03.73,01:07:06.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躲到丛林当缩头乌龟\N
Dialogue: 0,01:07:06.27,01:07:11.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你带领弟兄全力进攻\N
Dialogue: 0,01:07:12.11,01:07:15.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快进攻，这是命令\N
Dialogue: 0,01:07:24.55,01:07:27.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须违背你的命令\N
Dialogue: 0,01:07:46.44,01:07:49.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没有错，他下了命令\N
Dialogue: 0,01:07:52.61,01:07:57.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我请你让我派人到丛林搜查\N
Dialogue: 0,01:07:59.39,01:08:01.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在时间是\N
Dialogue: 0,01:08:01.22,01:08:03.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,13时21分25秒\N
Dialogue: 0,01:08:03.76,01:08:06.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两名证人听到我的话\N
Dialogue: 0,01:08:06.59,01:08:08.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你也找证人\N
Dialogue: 0,01:08:13.50,01:08:17.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别给我来律师那一套\N
Dialogue: 0,01:08:17.20,01:08:21.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是律师，这里却不是法庭\N
Dialogue: 0,01:08:21.31,01:08:23.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是战场，我们在打仗\N
Dialogue: 0,01:08:23.78,01:08:28.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我重复，我要你正面攻击\N
Dialogue: 0,01:08:29.62,01:08:32.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝率领弟兄正面攻击\N
Dialogue: 0,01:08:32.52,01:08:33.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这等于是自杀\N
Dialogue: 0,01:08:33.82,01:08:38.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和他们生活两年半\N不能命令他们送死
Dialogue: 0,01:08:39.03,01:08:39.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完毕\N
Dialogue: 0,01:08:48.80,01:08:51.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是很重大的决定\N
Dialogue: 0,01:08:55.44,01:08:59.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许你有理由这么做\N我要过去
Dialogue: 0,01:09:01.38,01:09:03.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是取消命令\N
Dialogue: 0,01:09:04.12,01:09:07.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过要是有特殊状况\N
Dialogue: 0,01:09:07.42,01:09:08.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会仔细考虑\N
Dialogue: 0,01:09:08.86,01:09:12.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们给我守在那儿等我来\N
Dialogue: 0,01:09:12.86,01:09:16.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能的话叫那些弟兄前进\N
Dialogue: 0,01:09:16.63,01:09:17.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完毕\N
Dialogue: 0,01:09:18.87,01:09:20.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（希腊语）\N
Dialogue: 0,01:09:30.78,01:09:33.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里都一样\N
Dialogue: 0,01:09:34.35,01:09:36.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就无处可躲\N
Dialogue: 0,01:09:40.12,01:09:43.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子，放轻松\N
Dialogue: 0,01:09:47.16,01:09:48.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,费夫呢？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:09:48.63,01:09:50.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这儿，费夫\N
Dialogue: 0,01:09:51.17,01:09:53.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,握住我的手\N
Dialogue: 0,01:09:54.13,01:09:55.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,握我的手\N
Dialogue: 0,01:10:03.31,01:10:09.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我快死了\N
Dialogue: 0,01:10:36.31,01:10:38.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连长\N
Dialogue: 0,01:11:27.56,01:11:29.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被埋在棺材里\N
Dialogue: 0,01:11:31.70,01:11:33.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掀不起棺盖\N
Dialogue: 0,01:11:36.34,01:11:38.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的处境进退两难\N
Dialogue: 0,01:11:38.94,01:11:42.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿上衣服，这不是海滩\N
Dialogue: 0,01:11:43.38,01:11:44.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻穿上\N
Dialogue: 0,01:11:44.81,01:11:48.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在指谁？去杀敌呀\N
Dialogue: 0,01:11:48.48,01:11:49.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前进\N
Dialogue: 0,01:12:00.46,01:12:03.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你趴在这儿什么也看不到\N
Dialogue: 0,01:12:09.44,01:12:10.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在观察\N
Dialogue: 0,01:12:10.94,01:12:12.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我派第一排上去\N
Dialogue: 0,01:12:12.74,01:12:14.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次有几个中弹？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:12:15.78,01:12:16.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N
Dialogue: 0,01:12:16.64,01:12:18.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个都没有？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:12:19.58,01:12:23.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这跟你说的情况不一样\N
Dialogue: 0,01:12:23.52,01:12:26.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五分钟前情况改变了\N
Dialogue: 0,01:12:31.26,01:12:33.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上尉，给我听好\N
Dialogue: 0,01:12:34.03,01:12:36.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要全力向前进攻\N
Dialogue: 0,01:12:36.73,01:12:39.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有问题吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:12:40.50,01:12:41.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在没有\N
Dialogue: 0,01:12:41.60,01:12:43.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，你得照我的方法\N
Dialogue: 0,01:12:43.97,01:12:47.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我来指挥\N
Dialogue: 0,01:12:47.37,01:12:50.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家上去，晚上得攻下来\N
Dialogue: 0,01:12:50.74,01:12:53.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面的火力还是很强\N
Dialogue: 0,01:13:01.89,01:13:04.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神啊，你到底看到什么？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:13:07.66,01:13:09.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我知道你看到什么\N
Dialogue: 0,01:13:13.50,01:13:16.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们全是尘土\N
Dialogue: 0,01:13:40.46,01:13:42.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留在这儿肯定送命\N
Dialogue: 0,01:13:42.70,01:13:43.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔\N
Dialogue: 0,01:13:44.50,01:13:47.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带六个弟兄上去探查\N
Dialogue: 0,01:13:53.51,01:13:56.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会掩护你们\N
Dialogue: 0,01:15:17.69,01:15:19.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们留下来\N
Dialogue: 0,01:15:21.43,01:15:23.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人去\N
Dialogue: 0,01:17:03.13,01:17:04.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\N
Dialogue: 0,01:17:10.34,01:17:12.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到我的身边\N
Dialogue: 0,01:18:22.94,01:18:25.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面有…\N
Dialogue: 0,01:18:25.05,01:18:28.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面有一座碉堡\N
Dialogue: 0,01:18:29.65,01:18:33.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总共有五支机关枪\N
Dialogue: 0,01:18:39.26,01:18:43.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻下那些乱石间的碉堡\N
Dialogue: 0,01:18:43.96,01:18:46.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能攻下这座山头\N
Dialogue: 0,01:18:48.87,01:18:50.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔说得没错\N
Dialogue: 0,01:18:51.10,01:18:54.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日本鬼子从上面\N
Dialogue: 0,01:18:54.64,01:18:58.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以扫射一千码内的目标\N
Dialogue: 0,01:18:59.45,01:19:02.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过他们漏掉这地方\N
Dialogue: 0,01:19:02.08,01:19:04.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是很严重的错误\N
Dialogue: 0,01:19:05.25,01:19:09.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得利用他们的疏失\N
Dialogue: 0,01:19:11.83,01:19:15.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你们筋疲力尽\N
Dialogue: 0,01:19:15.66,01:19:18.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水也没有送上来\N
Dialogue: 0,01:19:19.87,01:19:22.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，我向大家道歉\N
Dialogue: 0,01:19:23.84,01:19:26.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过明天若能攻下这座碉堡\N
Dialogue: 0,01:19:26.71,01:19:28.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就能占领山头\N
Dialogue: 0,01:19:31.24,01:19:33.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没有人自愿\N
Dialogue: 0,01:19:33.88,01:19:36.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去攻下那座碉堡\N
Dialogue: 0,01:19:36.15,01:19:37.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长官\N
Dialogue: 0,01:19:38.19,01:19:41.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意身先士卒回去作战\N
Dialogue: 0,01:19:42.02,01:19:42.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好，贝尔\N
Dialogue: 0,01:19:42.99,01:19:43.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上校，我也去\N
Dialogue: 0,01:19:43.92,01:19:44.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有你\N
Dialogue: 0,01:19:46.86,01:19:48.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很想率领突击队\N
Dialogue: 0,01:19:48.90,01:19:53.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正希望你去，约翰\N你来指挥
Dialogue: 0,01:19:53.13,01:19:54.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去\N
Dialogue: 0,01:19:54.07,01:19:56.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，你…你…\N
Dialogue: 0,01:19:56.47,01:19:59.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,够了，七个人够多了\N
Dialogue: 0,01:19:59.17,01:20:00.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备出发\N
Dialogue: 0,01:20:04.08,01:20:08.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道这一役有多重要吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:20:10.05,01:20:13.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻下这座岛，轰炸机就能降落\N
Dialogue: 0,01:20:13.49,01:20:17.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我军有一千英里的空中攻击力\N
Dialogue: 0,01:20:18.46,01:20:21.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瓜达康拉尔岛一役能决定胜负\N
Dialogue: 0,01:20:22.90,01:20:26.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不同意，一定得牺牲性命？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:20:26.20,01:20:27.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是，长官\N
Dialogue: 0,01:20:29.74,01:20:32.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你说过胜利的重要\N
Dialogue: 0,01:20:32.44,01:20:35.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认为牺牲多少弟兄才值得？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:20:35.91,01:20:37.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N
Dialogue: 0,01:20:44.18,01:20:47.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意牺牲你的弟兄吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:20:51.12,01:20:53.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多少？一个？两个？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:20:54.96,01:20:56.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二十个？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:20:58.20,01:21:01.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的连上一定会死人\N
Dialogue: 0,01:21:02.57,01:21:04.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你受不了\N
Dialogue: 0,01:21:05.11,01:21:07.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好让我知道\N
Dialogue: 0,01:21:07.94,01:21:09.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，你说得对\N
Dialogue: 0,01:21:10.08,01:21:11.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说得都对\N
Dialogue: 0,01:21:12.08,01:21:15.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，没事了\N
Dialogue: 0,01:21:17.88,01:21:19.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一件事\N
Dialogue: 0,01:21:20.95,01:21:25.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不必跟我说我说得对\N
Dialogue: 0,01:21:25.53,01:21:27.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有必要\N
Dialogue: 0,01:21:27.36,01:21:30.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是理所当然的\N
Dialogue: 0,01:21:30.10,01:21:31.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解散\N
Dialogue: 0,01:21:48.28,01:21:50.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为你感到遗憾\N
Dialogue: 0,01:21:51.85,01:21:52.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:21:52.52,01:21:53.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一点吧\N
Dialogue: 0,01:21:57.42,01:21:59.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这场战争会害死你\N
Dialogue: 0,01:22:03.06,01:22:07.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要自求多福，别想救别人\N
Dialogue: 0,01:22:09.17,01:22:13.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你拼命也救不了什么人\N
Dialogue: 0,01:22:26.19,01:22:30.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在乱世中一个人的力量很渺小\N
Dialogue: 0,01:22:36.46,01:22:38.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要白白送死\N
Dialogue: 0,01:22:43.14,01:22:46.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有另一个美好世界\N
Dialogue: 0,01:22:47.91,01:22:49.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是唯一的世界\N
Dialogue: 0,01:22:52.11,01:22:53.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有这座孤岛\N
Dialogue: 0,01:23:31.08,01:23:33.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧，让我死吧\N
Dialogue: 0,01:23:33.55,01:23:39.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁能决定别人的生死？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:23:41.43,01:23:43.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太荒谬了\N
Dialogue: 0,01:23:45.17,01:23:53.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看我，我身上没有中弹\N毫发未伤
Dialogue: 0,01:23:53.11,01:23:54.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:23:55.28,01:23:59.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们全都死了，我却站在这儿\N
Dialogue: 0,01:23:59.75,01:24:02.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一点事也没有\N
Dialogue: 0,01:24:22.40,01:24:24.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们\N
Dialogue: 0,01:24:30.98,01:24:32.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在一起\N
Dialogue: 0,01:24:43.66,01:24:45.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合而为一\N
Dialogue: 0,01:25:00.81,01:25:03.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水乳交融\N
Dialogue: 0,01:25:06.48,01:25:09.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分不出和我\N
Dialogue: 0,01:25:26.60,01:25:28.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱\N
Dialogue: 0,01:25:30.70,01:25:32.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在\N
Dialogue: 0,01:25:35.21,01:25:36.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在\N
Dialogue: 0,01:26:14.28,01:26:15.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您是我的明灯\N
Dialogue: 0,01:26:19.25,01:26:20.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的指引\N
Dialogue: 0,01:27:30.66,01:27:34.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在后面，要是攻破防线\N
Dialogue: 0,01:27:34.59,01:27:35.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就吹哨子通知我们冲上去\N
Dialogue: 0,01:27:37.36,01:27:39.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧，去杀敌吧\N
Dialogue: 0,01:29:37.58,01:29:39.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们留在底下\N
Dialogue: 0,01:29:40.02,01:29:44.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从上面叫出敌人方位\N
Dialogue: 0,01:29:44.69,01:29:48.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让炮兵密集轰炸这些岩石\N
Dialogue: 0,01:29:48.29,01:29:52.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再到大石旁找掩护\N
Dialogue: 0,01:29:53.93,01:29:55.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后从右翼进攻\N
Dialogue: 0,01:29:56.37,01:29:57.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:29:59.57,01:30:02.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…好…\N
Dialogue: 0,01:30:22.73,01:30:24.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方位1470\N
Dialogue: 0,01:30:26.00,01:30:27.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,座标ER7\N
Dialogue: 0,01:30:28.10,01:30:30.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左方一百码，距离两百码\N
Dialogue: 0,01:30:30.47,01:30:32.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炮兵部队，准备开炮\N
Dialogue: 0,01:30:33.01,01:30:36.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方位1470、座标ER7\N
Dialogue: 0,01:30:36.58,01:30:40.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左方一百码，距离两百码\N
Dialogue: 0,01:30:40.55,01:30:43.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炮轰机关枪，稍后再修正\N
Dialogue: 0,01:30:43.95,01:30:45.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到了\N
Dialogue: 0,01:31:00.73,01:31:02.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左25码、前50码\N
Dialogue: 0,01:31:04.07,01:31:06.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炮兵部队\N
Dialogue: 0,01:31:06.41,01:31:08.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左25码、前50码\N
Dialogue: 0,01:31:08.88,01:31:10.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备开炮\N
Dialogue: 0,01:31:36.04,01:31:37.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上吧\N
Dialogue: 0,01:31:52.62,01:31:55.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从右翼攻上山头\N
Dialogue: 0,01:31:55.96,01:31:59.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我信号再开枪或丢手榴弹\N
Dialogue: 0,01:31:59.69,01:32:01.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，咱们上\N
Dialogue: 0,01:32:05.93,01:32:07.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N
Dialogue: 0,01:32:16.94,01:32:17.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他没事吧？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:32:19.08,01:32:22.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能把他带走，怎么办？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:32:23.12,01:32:24.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能把他留下来\N
Dialogue: 0,01:32:24.78,01:32:26.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是同排弟兄，你陪他\N
Dialogue: 0,01:32:26.89,01:32:28.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们回来再接他\N
Dialogue: 0,01:32:28.82,01:32:30.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他还活着\N
Dialogue: 0,01:32:34.76,01:32:35.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他死了吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:32:35.86,01:32:36.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没有\N
Dialogue: 0,01:32:36.80,01:32:39.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陪着他，掩护我们\N
Dialogue: 0,01:32:39.13,01:32:40.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上吧\N
Dialogue: 0,01:33:05.49,01:33:06.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心后面\N
Dialogue: 0,01:33:22.68,01:33:24.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们被打得好惨\N
Dialogue: 0,01:33:53.87,01:33:55.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撤退\N
Dialogue: 0,01:34:01.61,01:34:02.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N
Dialogue: 0,01:34:52.40,01:34:53.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向左冲\N
Dialogue: 0,01:35:13.62,01:35:14.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心\N
Dialogue: 0,01:35:54.29,01:35:58.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安全了！安全了！\N
Dialogue: 0,01:36:49.01,01:36:50.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我滚出来\N
Dialogue: 0,01:36:51.28,01:36:52.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出来\N
Dialogue: 0,01:36:56.49,01:36:58.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想杀我们？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:37:05.76,01:37:07.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这人渣\N
Dialogue: 0,01:37:14.14,01:37:17.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狗娘养的\N
Dialogue: 0,01:37:42.20,01:37:44.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我杀死一个人\N
Dialogue: 0,01:38:19.34,01:38:21.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里好臭\N
Dialogue: 0,01:38:22.47,01:38:24.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么多死人\N
Dialogue: 0,01:38:24.34,01:38:25.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鼻孔里塞烟头\N
Dialogue: 0,01:39:49.46,01:39:52.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看他们逃命…\N
Dialogue: 0,01:39:52.90,01:39:54.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他们赶跑了\N
Dialogue: 0,01:39:54.63,01:39:55.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰，干得好\N
Dialogue: 0,01:39:55.93,01:39:58.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把他们打得落荒而逃\N
Dialogue: 0,01:39:58.20,01:40:00.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弟兄们都士气高涨\N
Dialogue: 0,01:40:00.44,01:40:02.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别打了\N
Dialogue: 0,01:40:03.01,01:40:06.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把犯人带来，交给情报部\N
Dialogue: 0,01:40:06.41,01:40:08.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们马上就来\N
Dialogue: 0,01:40:08.05,01:40:10.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浪费了很多时间，走吧\N
Dialogue: 0,01:40:10.32,01:40:13.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要推荐一些人接受勋章\N
Dialogue: 0,01:40:13.15,01:40:16.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会尽力向他们争取\N
Dialogue: 0,01:40:16.09,01:40:17.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后再说\N
Dialogue: 0,01:40:17.09,01:40:18.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我要你知道\N
Dialogue: 0,01:40:18.92,01:40:21.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会推荐你接受勋章\N
Dialogue: 0,01:40:21.49,01:40:23.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许是英勇奖章\N谢谢你，不过我…
Dialogue: 0,01:40:23.60,01:40:26.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你应得的\N
Dialogue: 0,01:40:26.13,01:40:28.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能争取到才是问题\N
Dialogue: 0,01:40:29.13,01:40:33.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能受勋对部队鼓舞很大\N
Dialogue: 0,01:40:33.94,01:40:35.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好赶快前进\N
Dialogue: 0,01:40:35.41,01:40:39.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加入别的连队攻上山头\N
Dialogue: 0,01:40:39.75,01:40:42.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想指挥B连吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:40:43.02,01:40:44.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然想\N
Dialogue: 0,01:40:44.22,01:40:48.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想扫你的兴\N要是没有食用水…
Dialogue: 0,01:40:48.39,01:40:50.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心水的问题\N
Dialogue: 0,01:40:52.26,01:40:57.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在士气如虹，不能中断\N
Dialogue: 0,01:40:57.56,01:41:01.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过几个小时就有食用水\N
Dialogue: 0,01:41:01.57,01:41:03.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会安排的\N
Dialogue: 0,01:41:03.97,01:41:07.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死，现在不能停下来\N
Dialogue: 0,01:41:07.51,01:41:09.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，长官\N
Dialogue: 0,01:41:09.41,01:41:10.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N
Dialogue: 0,01:41:11.71,01:41:16.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是有些人会脱水昏倒\N
Dialogue: 0,01:41:16.22,01:41:18.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就让他们昏倒\N
Dialogue: 0,01:41:21.42,01:41:22.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N
Dialogue: 0,01:41:23.36,01:41:26.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会死的\N
Dialogue: 0,01:41:26.16,01:41:28.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们也会被敌人杀死\N
Dialogue: 0,01:41:29.46,01:41:32.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们很坚强\N
Dialogue: 0,01:41:36.47,01:41:38.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弟兄们，走吧\N
Dialogue: 0,01:41:39.04,01:41:41.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一路上会有更多死人\N
Dialogue: 0,01:41:41.77,01:41:44.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底要不要上山头？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:41:47.81,01:41:52.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信现在能突破日军防线\N
Dialogue: 0,01:41:52.28,01:41:54.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要继续前进\N
Dialogue: 0,01:41:54.32,01:41:56.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日落时就能攻下山头\N
Dialogue: 0,01:41:57.36,01:42:00.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到他们全新的斗志吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:42:00.53,01:42:04.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得一鼓作气、乘胜追击\N
Dialogue: 0,01:42:05.73,01:42:09.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是稍微迟疑就会战败\N
Dialogue: 0,01:42:09.77,01:42:15.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是根本攻不上山头\N
Dialogue: 0,01:42:15.57,01:42:18.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊，我不能忍受失败\N
Dialogue: 0,01:42:20.15,01:42:22.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我等了一辈子\N
Dialogue: 0,01:42:22.48,01:42:27.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍气吞声这么久就为了这一刻\N
Dialogue: 0,01:42:27.19,01:42:29.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会半途而废\N
Dialogue: 0,01:42:33.33,01:42:37.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道被忽略的感受\N
Dialogue: 0,01:42:37.23,01:42:40.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚出军校，还很年轻\N
Dialogue: 0,01:42:40.77,01:42:42.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你生对时代了\N
Dialogue: 0,01:42:42.40,01:42:45.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我等了十五年才等到场战争\N
Dialogue: 0,01:42:52.28,01:42:55.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天你会了解\N
Dialogue: 0,01:43:00.19,01:43:02.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把你当儿子看待\N
Dialogue: 0,01:43:04.56,01:43:07.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道我儿子做什么吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:43:07.59,01:43:10.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他做鱼饵生意\N
Dialogue: 0,01:43:13.10,01:43:14.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你干得很好\N
Dialogue: 0,01:43:14.70,01:43:19.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要让你得到应得的荣誉\N
Dialogue: 0,01:43:21.54,01:43:22.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，长官\N
Dialogue: 0,01:43:25.78,01:43:26.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老天\N
Dialogue: 0,01:43:28.48,01:43:29.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死\N
Dialogue: 0,01:43:29.82,01:43:31.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要三名传令兵\N
Dialogue: 0,01:43:31.52,01:43:37.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去找水源，马上运过来\N
Dialogue: 0,01:43:39.39,01:43:41.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一小时后就全力进攻\N
Dialogue: 0,01:43:41.26,01:43:42.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能失败\N
Dialogue: 0,01:43:42.79,01:43:47.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人能阻止，晚上就得成功\N
Dialogue: 0,01:44:11.56,01:44:13.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看过死人吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:44:14.83,01:44:16.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多\N
Dialogue: 0,01:57:55.18,01:57:58.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人曾死在你怀里吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:57:58.55,01:58:00.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:58:14.10,01:58:16.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想引起事端\N
Dialogue: 0,01:58:16.67,01:58:20.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不想在服役记录中留下污点\N
Dialogue: 0,01:58:20.27,01:58:22.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该也不想\N
Dialogue: 0,01:58:22.21,01:58:25.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这和能力或胆量无关\N
Dialogue: 0,01:58:29.01,01:58:30.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看这座丛林\N
Dialogue: 0,01:58:31.42,01:58:34.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些藤蔓缠绕着大树\N
Dialogue: 0,01:58:34.65,01:58:36.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吞食一切\N
Dialogue: 0,01:58:39.16,01:58:41.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大自然很残酷\N
Dialogue: 0,01:58:50.67,01:58:56.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以申请调到华府的军法局\N
Dialogue: 0,01:58:56.54,01:58:59.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是律师，就说你生了病\N
Dialogue: 0,01:58:59.68,01:59:01.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得过疟疾吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:59:01.35,01:59:02.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N
Dialogue: 0,01:59:02.28,01:59:05.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓，我会安排的\N
Dialogue: 0,01:59:05.52,01:59:07.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正你会染上的\N
Dialogue: 0,01:59:07.59,01:59:10.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也会推荐你获颁银星勋章\N
Dialogue: 0,01:59:11.06,01:59:14.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会让你无法推辞\N
Dialogue: 0,01:59:15.83,01:59:18.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干脆也让你得紫心奖章\N
Dialogue: 0,01:59:21.37,01:59:22.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:59:23.17,01:59:28.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你脸上的疤\N和手上的伤口
Dialogue: 0,01:59:28.74,01:59:30.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我听好\N
Dialogue: 0,01:59:30.58,01:59:34.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟下一批伤兵离开\N
Dialogue: 0,01:59:34.55,01:59:38.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留下来对你没好处\N
Dialogue: 0,01:59:38.38,01:59:41.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这件事不说出去最好\N
Dialogue: 0,02:00:16.79,02:00:18.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是陶尔上校的宣布\N
Dialogue: 0,02:00:20.29,02:00:23.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的胜利带来最高的荣耀\N
Dialogue: 0,02:00:24.80,02:00:28.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是瓜达康拉尔岛役的转捩点\N
Dialogue: 0,02:00:29.77,02:00:34.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天师长会亲自来检阅前线\N
Dialogue: 0,02:00:35.61,02:00:40.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接防部队会来换班\N
Dialogue: 0,02:00:41.55,02:00:44.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为全营弟兄\N
Dialogue: 0,02:00:44.35,02:00:46.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,争取到一星期的假\N
Dialogue: 0,02:00:50.82,02:00:51.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样\N
Dialogue: 0,02:02:47.67,02:02:49.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长夜漫漫\N
Dialogue: 0,02:02:51.74,02:02:53.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,度日如年\N
Dialogue: 0,02:02:57.08,02:02:59.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正值青春年华\N
Dialogue: 0,02:03:03.05,02:03:06.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站在新世界的边缘\N
Dialogue: 0,02:03:16.87,02:03:19.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本来想去看你们\N
Dialogue: 0,02:03:19.60,02:03:21.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过…\N
Dialogue: 0,02:03:24.71,02:03:26.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想一个人静一下\N
Dialogue: 0,02:03:41.43,02:03:43.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要谢谢你\N
Dialogue: 0,02:03:47.60,02:03:50.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要求进行包抄行动\N
Dialogue: 0,02:03:52.34,02:03:54.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为我们着想\N
Dialogue: 0,02:03:56.34,02:03:57.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们团结一致\N
Dialogue: 0,02:04:03.48,02:04:07.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不该被调走，这不公平\N
Dialogue: 0,02:04:11.56,02:04:13.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我并不同意\N
Dialogue: 0,02:04:16.03,02:04:18.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最难的是\N
Dialogue: 0,02:04:19.66,02:04:21.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道这么做有没有用\N
Dialogue: 0,02:04:23.90,02:04:25.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这才是最难的\N
Dialogue: 0,02:04:28.57,02:04:31.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过无所谓，我不在乎\N
Dialogue: 0,02:04:31.58,02:04:33.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴能离开\N
Dialogue: 0,02:04:34.71,02:04:36.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很高兴\N
Dialogue: 0,02:04:36.81,02:04:38.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是能提出申诉\N
Dialogue: 0,02:04:38.78,02:04:39.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:04:41.65,02:04:43.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么用？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:04:46.06,02:04:47.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我想走\N
Dialogue: 0,02:04:50.03,02:04:52.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别管它，算了吧\N
Dialogue: 0,02:04:58.54,02:05:00.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（希腊语）\N
Dialogue: 0,02:05:05.08,02:05:06.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:05:09.95,02:05:12.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们像是我的孩子\N
Dialogue: 0,02:05:23.79,02:05:25.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是我的孩子\N
Dialogue: 0,02:05:26.93,02:05:28.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的孩子\N
Dialogue: 0,02:05:32.90,02:05:34.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们活在我心中\N
Dialogue: 0,02:05:38.94,02:05:40.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远与我同在\N
Dialogue: 0,02:05:57.13,02:05:59.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忘不了战争的可怕\N
Dialogue: 0,02:06:03.67,02:06:06.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悲剧不断重演\N
Dialogue: 0,02:06:11.94,02:06:14.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战争不能给我们荣耀\N
Dialogue: 0,02:06:15.51,02:06:17.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只会把人变成野狗\N
Dialogue: 0,02:06:23.72,02:06:26.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,荼毒我们的心灵\N
Dialogue: 0,02:07:29.95,02:07:31.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的妻子\N
Dialogue: 0,02:07:34.73,02:07:38.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战争的丑陋和血腥暴力\N
Dialogue: 0,02:07:38.83,02:07:42.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会让人丧失良知\N
Dialogue: 0,02:07:50.71,02:07:52.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很想保持纯真\N
Dialogue: 0,02:07:55.91,02:07:58.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想以原来的我回到身边\N
Dialogue: 0,02:08:06.89,02:08:09.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们该如何获得宁静？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:08:13.33,02:08:15.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回到青山绿水间？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:08:26.24,02:08:27.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真爱\N
Dialogue: 0,02:08:36.99,02:08:38.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底来自何方？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:08:47.30,02:08:49.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁燃起我们心中的爱火？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:08:56.64,02:08:58.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战争无法熄灭它\N
Dialogue: 0,02:09:00.21,02:09:01.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是征服它\N
Dialogue: 0,02:09:09.95,02:09:11.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾是个囚犯\N
Dialogue: 0,02:09:16.43,02:09:18.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我自由\N
Dialogue: 0,02:09:23.47,02:09:25.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管你受过多少训练\N
Dialogue: 0,02:09:26.67,02:09:28.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是多么小心\N
Dialogue: 0,02:09:30.01,02:09:32.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要运气不好就会阵亡\N
Dialogue: 0,02:09:33.44,02:09:35.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管你是谁\N
Dialogue: 0,02:09:36.68,02:09:38.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是多么骁勇善战\N
Dialogue: 0,02:09:40.82,02:09:43.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心就会被杀死\N
Dialogue: 0,02:09:55.97,02:09:57.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看着那个人死去\N
Dialogue: 0,02:09:59.94,02:10:01.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一点感觉都没有\N
Dialogue: 0,02:10:05.21,02:10:07.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对一切都不在乎\N
Dialogue: 0,02:10:12.78,02:10:15.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听起来很幸福\N
Dialogue: 0,02:10:19.16,02:10:21.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有那种感觉\N
Dialogue: 0,02:10:22.79,02:10:24.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻木不仁的感觉\N
Dialogue: 0,02:10:25.90,02:10:27.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你们不一样\N
Dialogue: 0,02:10:32.14,02:10:34.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许是因为我看得太多\N
Dialogue: 0,02:10:37.81,02:10:40.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就失去感觉\N
Dialogue: 0,02:11:23.79,02:11:26.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我入伍后就没碰过女人\N
Dialogue: 0,02:11:28.36,02:11:30.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或跟女人说过话\N
Dialogue: 0,02:11:34.40,02:11:36.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想\N
Dialogue: 0,02:11:37.30,02:11:39.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想有欲念\N
Dialogue: 0,02:12:17.17,02:12:22.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚伯罕，你的信\N史铁，叫他来
Dialogue: 0,02:12:24.85,02:12:29.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔…贝尔…\N
Dialogue: 0,02:12:34.66,02:12:36.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的杰克\N
Dialogue: 0,02:12:38.50,02:12:40.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认识一个空军上尉\N
Dialogue: 0,02:12:41.67,02:12:43.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱上他\N
Dialogue: 0,02:12:46.44,02:12:48.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟你离婚嫁给他\N
Dialogue: 0,02:12:55.18,02:12:59.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以拒绝，但我还是要说\N
Dialogue: 0,02:12:59.05,02:13:01.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟我们曾夫妻一场\N
Dialogue: 0,02:13:08.39,02:13:09.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我\N
Dialogue: 0,02:13:11.36,02:13:14.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我太寂寞了\N
Dialogue: 0,02:13:35.25,02:13:36.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会再见\N
Dialogue: 0,02:13:40.19,02:13:44.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定会再见面的\N
Dialogue: 0,02:13:53.04,02:13:56.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我无权跟你这么说\N
Dialogue: 0,02:13:56.17,02:13:57.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我忍不住\N
Dialogue: 0,02:13:58.34,02:14:00.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,习惯成自然\N
Dialogue: 0,02:14:02.65,02:14:06.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你曾是我最好的朋友\N
Dialogue: 0,02:14:09.45,02:14:11.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮助我离开你\N
Dialogue: 0,02:15:38.68,02:15:40.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:16:53.15,02:16:54.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们曾是一家人\N
Dialogue: 0,02:16:58.15,02:17:00.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得已被拆散\N
Dialogue: 0,02:17:03.89,02:17:06.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们自相残杀\N
Dialogue: 0,02:17:09.37,02:17:11.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,断送彼此的生路\N
Dialogue: 0,02:17:21.28,02:17:24.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们怎么会失去善良本性？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:17:25.62,02:17:27.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泯灭天理良知\N
Dialogue: 0,02:17:30.39,02:17:33.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将人性弃之不顾\N
Dialogue: 0,02:17:53.31,02:17:56.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们为什么无法升华？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:17:56.65,02:17:58.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,达到光荣的巅峰？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:18:00.38,02:18:05.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是日军你早就死了\N
Dialogue: 0,02:18:07.86,02:18:09.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得留下来？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:18:11.49,02:18:14.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，我会拖累他们\N
Dialogue: 0,02:18:15.83,02:18:17.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不介意\N
Dialogue: 0,02:18:18.74,02:18:21.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医官帮我包扎得很好\N
Dialogue: 0,02:18:22.24,02:18:23.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有很多弹药\N
Dialogue: 0,02:18:26.58,02:18:29.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定会有人来接我\N
Dialogue: 0,02:18:33.95,02:18:35.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你伤不轻\N
Dialogue: 0,02:18:35.32,02:18:36.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,膝盖中弹\N
Dialogue: 0,02:18:36.49,02:18:37.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N
Dialogue: 0,02:18:38.39,02:18:40.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不必再打仗了\N
Dialogue: 0,02:18:46.03,02:18:47.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这儿干嘛？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:18:47.93,02:18:51.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要回到连上\N
Dialogue: 0,02:18:52.94,02:18:54.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N
Dialogue: 0,02:18:55.61,02:18:57.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟大伙儿问好\N
Dialogue: 0,02:18:58.01,02:18:59.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以跟我来\N
Dialogue: 0,02:19:00.61,02:19:02.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我扶你\N
Dialogue: 0,02:19:03.91,02:19:06.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不了，这里很好\N
Dialogue: 0,02:19:07.02,02:19:09.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很安静\N
Dialogue: 0,02:19:11.05,02:19:14.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会拖累你，部队会接我\N
Dialogue: 0,02:19:18.26,02:19:20.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会提醒他们\N
Dialogue: 0,02:19:20.73,02:19:22.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N
Dialogue: 0,02:20:58.03,02:20:59.65,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威特\N
Dialogue: 0,02:21:04.70,02:21:06.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天你惹了什么麻烦？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:21:07.84,02:21:09.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:21:10.81,02:21:13.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是最爱惹麻烦吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:21:14.18,02:21:16.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫你向左你偏偏向右\N
Dialogue: 0,02:21:23.59,02:21:25.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么这么爱惹麻烦？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:21:28.49,02:21:31.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很关心我，对吧？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:21:32.20,02:21:34.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都这么觉得\N
Dialogue: 0,02:21:36.40,02:21:38.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么装得冷酷无情？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:21:40.17,02:21:43.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时我跟你聊得很愉快\N
Dialogue: 0,02:21:44.01,02:21:45.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隔一天\N
Dialogue: 0,02:21:45.61,02:21:47.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就像没见过面似的\N
Dialogue: 0,02:22:01.82,02:22:03.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好孤单的房子\N
Dialogue: 0,02:22:06.63,02:22:08.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会觉得孤单吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:22:08.97,02:22:10.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有在人群中\N
Dialogue: 0,02:22:19.58,02:22:22.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还是有美好的信念，对吧？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:22:30.69,02:22:32.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么办得到？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:22:34.22,02:22:36.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就像是魔法师\N
Dialogue: 0,02:22:45.50,02:22:48.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你眼中仍有一丝良知\N
Dialogue: 0,02:23:12.83,02:23:17.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人看到死去小鸟的眼中\N只有无言的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,02:23:21.04,02:23:24.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过死亡是无情的\N
Dialogue: 0,02:23:26.18,02:23:28.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死神在嘲笑他\N
Dialogue: 0,02:23:37.69,02:23:40.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人看着同一只小鸟\N
Dialogue: 0,02:23:43.16,02:23:45.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却看到生命光辉\N
Dialogue: 0,02:23:50.13,02:23:52.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心中充满喜悦\N
Dialogue: 0,02:24:50.03,02:24:52.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得马上撤退\N
Dialogue: 0,01:44:16.83,01:44:18.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟死狗没两样\N
Dialogue: 0,01:44:20.27,01:44:22.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有这种想法\N
Dialogue: 0,01:44:27.17,01:44:28.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们就像猪肉一样\N
Dialogue: 0,01:44:45.36,01:44:49.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们代表正义和善良吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:44:51.30,01:44:54.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是否有信心？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:44:56.70,01:44:58.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受到大家爱护？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:45:01.21,01:45:03.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你们一样\N
Dialogue: 0,01:45:06.81,01:45:10.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们以为自己比较有良知…\N
Dialogue: 0,01:45:11.98,01:45:13.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…或是善良吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:49:13.46,01:49:17.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趴下来，趴下来\N
Dialogue: 0,01:49:28.17,01:49:32.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我趴下来\N快点
Dialogue: 0,01:50:32.80,01:50:34.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么可怕的邪恶\N
Dialogue: 0,01:50:37.54,01:50:39.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它来自哪里？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:50:44.18,01:50:46.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会潜伏在世上？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:50:58.10,01:51:02.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原因和根源到底是什么？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:51:06.74,01:51:08.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是谁造成的？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:51:11.21,01:51:13.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁在屠杀众生\N
Dialogue: 0,01:51:17.22,01:51:20.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剥夺我们的生命之火\N
Dialogue: 0,01:51:24.26,01:51:27.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘲笑我们对人间的依恋\N
Dialogue: 0,01:51:54.09,01:51:57.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战争对地球有利吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:51:59.02,01:52:04.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它能滋长万物、孕育众生吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:52:08.90,01:52:11.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝也有黑暗的一面？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:52:17.71,01:52:20.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,k是否也感受邪恶力量？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:52:26.18,01:52:28.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你开膛剖肚\N
Dialogue: 0,01:52:32.36,01:52:34.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你死定了\N
Dialogue: 0,01:52:46.44,01:52:48.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到那些鸟吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:52:50.21,01:52:52.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它们会把你生吞活剥\N
Dialogue: 0,01:52:57.38,01:53:00.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你下地狱就回不来\N
Dialogue: 0,01:53:07.06,01:53:10.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（日语）\N
Dialogue: 0,01:54:12.16,01:54:13.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你对我有意义吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,01:54:20.06,01:54:21.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫无意义\N
Dialogue: 0,01:56:43.41,01:56:44.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐下来\N
Dialogue: 0,01:56:55.59,01:56:58.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,史塔，我要将你革职\N
Dialogue: 0,01:57:01.46,01:57:04.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,班中尉会取代你\N
Dialogue: 0,01:57:06.03,01:57:07.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他说了\N
Dialogue: 0,01:57:18.41,01:57:20.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想这么做\N
Dialogue: 0,01:57:21.45,01:57:23.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是很困难的决定\N
Dialogue: 0,01:57:27.39,01:57:29.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的心不够狠\N
Dialogue: 0,01:57:30.39,01:57:32.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你心太软了\N
Dialogue: 0,01:57:32.72,01:57:35.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不够心狠手辣\N
Dialogue: 0,01:57:40.03,01:57:44.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的心意已定，没什么好说\N
Dialogue: 0,01:57:45.57,01:57:48.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想让我的弟兄送死\N
Dialogue: 0,02:24:52.73,02:24:56.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟指挥部说过吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:24:56.83,02:24:57.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N
Dialogue: 0,02:24:57.77,02:25:01.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们知道我们在这儿吗？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:25:02.37,02:25:03.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们死定了\N
Dialogue: 0,02:25:04.37,02:25:05.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这要由我决定\N
Dialogue: 0,02:25:07.41,02:25:11.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得派人去看敌军有多近\N
Dialogue: 0,02:25:12.08,02:25:14.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吗？很容易\N
Dialogue: 0,02:25:15.35,02:25:18.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,韦德，呼叫指挥部\N
Dialogue: 0,02:25:18.92,02:25:20.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炮声越来越近\N
Dialogue: 0,02:25:20.82,02:25:22.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有讯号\N
Dialogue: 0,02:25:24.63,02:25:28.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得派人查出原因\N
Dialogue: 0,02:25:29.33,02:25:32.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和敌人有多近\N
Dialogue: 0,02:25:32.14,02:25:33.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\N
Dialogue: 0,02:25:34.27,02:25:36.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N
Dialogue: 0,02:25:40.14,02:25:42.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你\N
Dialogue: 0,02:25:43.18,02:25:44.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去\N
Dialogue: 0,02:25:45.78,02:25:47.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,费夫，你要去\N
Dialogue: 0,02:25:52.26,02:25:55.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老古，你也去\N
Dialogue: 0,02:25:56.09,02:25:57.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点\N
Dialogue: 0,02:25:57.36,02:25:58.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也去\N
Dialogue: 0,02:25:58.83,02:26:02.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这整个任务都不对\N
Dialogue: 0,02:26:02.27,02:26:04.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是他们全力进攻\N
Dialogue: 0,02:26:04.43,02:26:06.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们肯定没命\N
Dialogue: 0,02:26:06.97,02:26:09.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不必去，别人会去\N
Dialogue: 0,02:26:09.31,02:26:11.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要去\N
Dialogue: 0,02:26:11.34,02:26:15.14,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万一出事我要在场\N
Dialogue: 0,02:26:15.18,02:26:17.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，顺着河走\N
Dialogue: 0,02:26:17.48,02:26:20.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丛林很浓密，小心点\N
Dialogue: 0,02:26:20.25,02:26:21.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会的\N
Dialogue: 0,02:26:22.35,02:26:24.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝好运，威特\N
Dialogue: 0,02:26:24.42,02:26:26.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,费夫，你没事吧？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:27:54.08,02:27:55.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌军的增援部队\N
Dialogue: 0,02:27:58.25,02:28:02.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得回去告诉连长\N
Dialogue: 0,02:28:06.29,02:28:07.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N
Dialogue: 0,02:28:24.87,02:28:26.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我中弹了\N
Dialogue: 0,02:29:25.50,02:29:28.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人得留下来阻挡敌军\N
Dialogue: 0,02:29:35.34,02:29:37.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会有事的\N
Dialogue: 0,02:29:42.49,02:29:45.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是活不久了\N
Dialogue: 0,02:29:45.59,02:29:49.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们回去吧\N
Dialogue: 0,02:29:50.46,02:29:52.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧\N
Dialogue: 0,02:30:14.25,02:30:15.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威特\N
Dialogue: 0,02:31:02.36,02:31:03.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们来了\N
Dialogue: 0,02:31:05.77,02:31:08.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得走了，你不要\N
Dialogue: 0,02:31:08.04,02:31:13.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到枪声就躲起来\N
Dialogue: 0,02:31:13.64,02:31:15.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后再顺着河走下去\N
Dialogue: 0,02:31:55.68,02:31:56.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老古呢？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:31:58.02,02:31:59.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快撤退，敌人来了\N
Dialogue: 0,02:32:00.46,02:32:01.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撤退\N
Dialogue: 0,02:32:04.16,02:32:06.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威特呢？威特在哪儿？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:32:13.07,02:32:14.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,费夫，威特呢？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:32:18.67,02:32:22.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威特在哪儿？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:33:08.86,02:33:10.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（日语）\N
Dialogue: 0,02:36:55.92,02:36:58.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的生命光辉呢？\N
Dialogue: 0,02:37:21.11,02:37:24.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你们在喝私酿酒\N
Dialogue: 0,02:37:25.08,02:37:26.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系\N
Dialogue: 0,02:37:26.68,02:37:28.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是谎言…\N
Dialogue: 0,02:37:28.05,02:37:31.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我的部队可以尽管喝酒\N
Dialogue: 0,02:37:31.92,02:37:34.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…你见到和听到的一切\N
Dialogue: 0,02:37:34.36,02:37:38.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能执行任务就没问题\N
Dialogue: 0,02:37:38.59,02:37:40.39,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是不行…\N
Dialogue: 0,02:37:40.43,02:37:42.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…他就会有麻烦\N
Dialogue: 0,02:37:42.50,02:37:44.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们都在说谎\N
Dialogue: 0,02:37:44.53,02:37:46.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是个注重家庭的人\N
Dialogue: 0,02:37:46.57,02:37:48.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家才会在一起\N
Dialogue: 0,02:37:49.61,02:37:51.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是一家人\N
Dialogue: 0,02:37:52.64,02:37:54.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是父亲\N
Dialogue: 0,02:37:55.54,02:37:58.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副连长就是母亲\N
Dialogue: 0,02:37:58.71,02:38:01.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们一个接一个来\N
Dialogue: 0,02:38:01.78,02:38:04.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们都是我的孩子\N
Dialogue: 0,02:38:05.02,02:38:08.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一家之主是父亲\N
Dialogue: 0,02:38:08.76,02:38:12.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男主外女主内，这就是规矩\N
Dialogue: 0,02:38:13.63,02:38:16.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你们想见我\N
Dialogue: 0,02:38:16.13,02:38:17.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们被困在棺材里\N
Dialogue: 0,02:38:17.57,02:38:18.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有任何事\N
Dialogue: 0,02:38:18.70,02:38:19.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,移动的棺材\N
Dialogue: 0,02:38:19.84,02:38:22.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都会在\N
Dialogue: 0,02:38:22.44,02:38:24.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战争在圣诞节前不会结束\N
Dialogue: 0,02:38:24.81,02:38:26.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还要很久才能回家\N
Dialogue: 0,02:38:27.58,02:38:29.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们要我们牺牲\N
Dialogue: 0,02:38:31.91,02:38:33.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或相信他们的谎言\N
Dialogue: 0,02:38:39.22,02:38:42.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只有一个办法\N
Dialogue: 0,02:38:44.59,02:38:47.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到自己的出路\N
Dialogue: 0,02:38:49.77,02:38:52.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃到属于自己的小岛\N
Dialogue: 0,02:39:05.45,02:39:08.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这一生若不相信上帝\N
Dialogue: 0,02:39:09.22,02:39:11.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将会有所缺憾\N
Dialogue: 0,02:39:19.90,02:39:24.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝怜悯我，我就属于k\N
Dialogue: 0,02:40:13.98,02:40:19.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只期望有一天能回家\N
Dialogue: 0,02:40:19.66,02:40:21.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你有何打算\N
Dialogue: 0,02:40:22.66,02:40:26.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃了这么多苦，我已经觉悟\N
Dialogue: 0,02:40:26.30,02:40:29.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还年轻，不过历经苦难\N
Dialogue: 0,02:40:30.53,02:40:32.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我准备好好活下去\N
Dialogue: 0,02:40:32.83,02:40:37.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸常说，苦尽甘来\N
Dialogue: 0,02:40:37.84,02:40:41.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年轻人的日子不应该那么苦\N
Dialogue: 0,02:40:42.34,02:40:46.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我猜最苦的已经熬过去了\N
Dialogue: 0,02:40:46.82,02:40:48.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,往后会渐入佳境\N
Dialogue: 0,02:40:49.02,02:40:50.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的愿望\N
Dialogue: 0,02:40:51.32,02:40:52.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定能够实现\N
Dialogue: 0,02:40:54.69,02:40:56.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我长大了\N
Dialogue: 0,02:40:57.89,02:41:00.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我变得比较成熟\N
Dialogue: 0,02:41:00.90,02:41:03.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们曾经一起相处\N
